{
  "stem": "23626.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sisters always tell me, thanks to you-- and my oldest sister was a little bit upset that I was not in the book.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's about time that I bring you out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the movie was based on the book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened with the book--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was meaning But that was after the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened with the first book where, you know, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Keneally wrote-- OK-- When they started to gather people as witnesses for the book, they came to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They contacted me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was about two-- not quite two and a half months after I lost my husband.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19-- 1980.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I couldn't talk about concentration camp at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, would I-- would I-- if I would know that Helen is not around, I probably would say, somebody has to talk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there were only two of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I knew Helen lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew she-- whatever she will tell, that will apply the same to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe she remembers few more incidents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe I remember a few more that apply to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But basically, we were like sisters, all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, she-- she protected me sometimes, because she spoke very well German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I managed, and I learned quick because I had to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I felt, well, you know, they only can take one character, not two or three, because otherwise the book would never end, and-- and-- and the stories would never end.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, later, with the movie, I was told that they will put two-- you have a scene there with two maids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is one scene, supposedly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, it's based on the book.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
